    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil Wickramasinghe for the post of President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe has won the election of the eighth Executive President of Sri Lanka.",
        "Out of the votes cast, Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe got 134 votes and Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma could get only 82 votes.",
        "The empty seat next to Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, who is the Acting President, is next to the President of the Parliament. This photo was taken at the nominations ceremony yesterday. Today, Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe won the election for the chair."
      ],
